version_description: Backup Reminders, Contact Us and minor bug fixes

• Support for Turkish Language (Thank you mert özer)
• Stability Improvements

• Export contacts in CSV
• Fixed bug of missing file when exporting from backup history
• Turkish translation minor enhancements

• Import/Export contacts via CSV file
• Updated Turkish texts (Thanks mert!)

• Support for Exporting & Importing multiple phone numbers and email in CSV
• Sorting contacts by first name when importing from CSV
• Localized to France, Italian and Afrikaans

• Support for iOS 13 dark mode
• Bug Fixes
